## Description
The **Extract Events (TR) **task allows to extract data from the Tracking &amp; Reporting software service.

> Note

This task will only extract data from the T&amp;R environment configured for the application.

## Configuration
**![](data:image/png;base64,)**

- In the **Alias **field, enter the name of the task that will be displayed in the workflow.

- In the **Customer **field, enter the name of the required T&amp;R client.

- In the **Procedure **field, enter the name of the required T&amp;R procedure.

> Note

The input and output formats are the same as in the Doxee Platform 2 integration. For more information, see: [Use Case 3 - Tracking &amp; Reporting](https://code.doxee.com/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=17115822).
